'''Uridium''' was a volatile [[Ore/Legends|ore]] found in trace quantities on the [[Moon/Legends|moon]] of [[Uridia]]. It could be refined to enhance the effects of [[Blaster/Legends|laser weapons]], but it was dangerous to handle.

